con oo-ui-image-invert'></span><span class='oo-ui-labelElement-label'>डाउनलोड</span><span class='oo-ui-indicatorElement-indicator oo-ui-indicatorElement-noIndicator oo-ui-image-invert'></span></a></span></div>
		</div>

						<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">विकिस्रोतः तः</div>
